data.description: SELLER SAYS THEY WILL ENTERTAIN ALL OFFERS!! Introducing this fabulous duplex, an extraordinary investment for those eyeing a short-term rental-friendly property. Situated just two blocks from the Gulf of Mexico, this gem offers the ultimate beach lifestyle with the convenience of city living.Prime Location: Only two blocks from the Gulf of Mexico, this duplex is a beach lover's dream, providing easy access to sun, sand, and surf.Top-Notch Upgrades: Featuring a roof replaced in 2019, a new HVAC system in 2022, new fencing for both units, and brand new appliances in unit 6402, this property is ready for immediate enjoyment.One-Parcel Ownership: This duplex is one parcel, allowing one owner for the entire dwelling. This structure simplifies exterior repairs and upgrades, streamlining property management.Generous Space: With 4 bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms, 2 half baths, and a total of 2,148 square feet, there's ample room for guests to unwind and relax.Designed for Privacy: A thoughtfully designed privacy fence divides the duplex equally in the backyard, ensuring renters have their own private oasis.Beach Access: The Gulf of Mexico is just a stroll away, perfect for beach-combing, sunbathing, and water sports.Local Dining & Shopping: Discover a variety of restaurants, boutiques, and entertainment venues within close proximity.Outdoor Adventures: Enjoy fishing, boating, and exploring nature trails, all just minutes from your doorstep.Whether you're an investor seeking a profitable rental property or a homeowner looking for a coastal haven, this duplex is a must-see. Don't miss the chance to own a piece of Panama City Beach's vibrant community. This property is a three minute drive to beach access 12 and an 8 minute walk.Contact us to schedule a tour today, and let 6402 Beach Dr. welcome you home!VA ASSUMABLE LOAN.  2021 rental income was $73,439.78, 2022 $56,550.12 as one unit underwent upgrades.
